bill.title: Health.
bill.description: An act to add Section 293 to the Financial Code, to amend Sections 1250, 1265.5, 1266, 1275.3, 1324.20, 1326, 1337, 1418, 1567.50, 104820, 105250, 116565, 125175, 130500, 130507, 130509, and 130543 of, to amend and repeal Section 125165 of, and to add Sections 125155.1, 125157, and 125166 to, the Health and Safety Code, to amend Section 12739 of the Insurance Code, and to amend Sections 4107, 4684.60, 4684.74, 4684.75, 7502.5, 14005.40, 14007.9, 14011.2, 14087.9, 14105.191, 14105.436, 14105.45, 14110.55, 14126.033, 14132, 14132.951, 14166.20, 14166.225, 14166.23, 14166.245, 14495.10, and 14526.1 of, to add Sections 5783, 14005.50, 14013.5, 14105.455, 14105.46, 14132.20, 14132.952, 14166.115, 14522.4, 14525.1, 14526.2, and 14550.6 to, and to repeal Section 14522.3, 14526.1, and 14550.5 of, the Welfare and Institutions Code, relating to health, and declaring the urgency thereof, to take effect immediately.

history.action: From printer. Without reference to committee. Ordered to second reading. Read second time. To third reading.
Read third time, passed, and to Senate. (Ayes 47. Noes 2. Page 25.)
In Senate. Read first time. To Com. on RLS. for assignment.
Withdrawn from committee. Ordered placed on second reading file. Read second time. To third reading.

Read third time and amended. Joint Rule 10.5 suspended. (Ayes 37. Noes 1. Page 43.) Senate Rule 29.3 suspended. (Ayes 24. Noes 12. Page 43.) Read third time. Urgency clause adopted. Passed and to Assembly. (Ayes 29. Noes 11. Page 52.)
In Assembly. Concurrence in Senate amendments pending. Assembly Rule 77 suspended. Urgency clause adopted. Senate amendments concurred in. To enrollment. (Ayes 57. Noes 20. Page 57.)
Enrolled and to the Governor at 4:30 p.m.
Chaptered by Secretary of State. Chapter 5, Statutes of 2009-10 Fourth Extraordinary Session.
